Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.10,0:00:42.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,1887年  羅馬尼亞西部  特蘭西瓦尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:56.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,它是活的  它活過來了\N{\rENG}It's alive. It's alive. It's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.92,0:01:15.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,他在那兒 用力  再用力\N{\rENG}There he is! Hit it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.16,0:01:26.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,成功了\N{\rENG}Success!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:29.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,伯爵  原來是你\N{\rENG}Count, it's just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.43,0:01:33.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,你差點就失敗了  維克多\N{\rENG}I was beginning to lose faith, Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:38.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,只可惜你的成功…\N{\rENG}A pity your moment of triumph is being spoiled...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:41.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,卻因為盜墓引起公憤\N{\rENG}over a little thing like grave robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.35,0:01:43.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rENG}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:45.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,我必須逃離此地\N{\rENG}I must escape this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.95,0:01:48.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,你想逃到哪裡?\N{\rENG}Where are you going to run, Victor?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.86,0:01:54.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,你的實驗品…\N{\rENG}Your peculiar experiments have made you unwelcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.43,0:01:56.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,讓你成為眾矢之的\N{\rENG}in most of the civilized world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.96,0:02:01.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,我要帶他逃得遠遠的\N{\rENG}I'll take him away, far away, where no one will ever find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.07,0:02:02.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,不  維克多\N{\rENG}No, no, Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.63,0:02:06.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,我要接管他\N{\rENG}The time has come for me to take command of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:08.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,什麼?\N{\rENG}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.51,0:02:11.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,不然我為什麼把城堡借給你\N{\rENG}Why do you think I brought you here? Gave you this castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:14.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,-為你建造實驗室? -你說…\N{\rENG}-Equipped your laboratory? -You said....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.68,0:02:18.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,-你相信我的實驗 -沒錯\N{\rENG}-You said you believed in my work. -And I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:23.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,但是你自己也說過\N{\rENG}But now that it is, as you yourself have said...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.52,0:02:26.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是科學…\N{\rENG}a triumph of science...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.63,0:02:29.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,戰勝上帝的鐵證\N{\rENG}over God...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.16,0:02:36.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,我要用來完成我的目的\N{\rENG}it must now serve my purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:41.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,什麼目的?\N{\rENG}What purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:55.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,老天爺!\N{\rENG}Good God!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.62,0:02:59.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,我寧願死也不會幫你\N{\rENG}I would kill myself before helping in such a task.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:02.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,去死吧!我不需要你了\N{\rENG}Feel free. I don't actually need you anymore, Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.79,0:03:04.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,我只需要他\N{\rENG}I just need him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:07.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,他才是關鍵\N{\rENG}He is the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:11.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不能讓他助紂為虐\N{\rENG}I could never allow him to be used for such evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.34,0:03:12.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,我可以\N{\rENG}I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:16.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的新娘非要他不可\N{\rENG}In fact, my brides are insisting upon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:22.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,伊果  幫助我\N{\rENG}Igor, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:25.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,你一向對我很好  博士\N{\rENG}You have been so kind to me, Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:28.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,體諒我  關心我\N{\rENG}caring, thoughtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:31.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,但是他付我錢\N{\rENG}But he pays me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,退後\N{\rENG}Stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:39.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,你是殺不了我的\N{\rENG}You can't kill me, Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.44,0:03:47.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,我早就死了\N{\rENG}I'm already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:45.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,科學怪人\N{\rENG}Dr. Frankenstein!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.17,0:04:51.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,他要去磨坊  來吧!\N{\rENG}Look, it's headed for the windmill! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:35.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,苦艾酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.61,0:05:38.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,放火燒了它\N{\rENG}Burn it! Burn it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:51.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,聖經
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.98,0:06:45.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,吸血鬼\N{\rENG}Vampires.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:48.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,-快跑  快逃命 -吸血鬼!\N{\rENG}-Run for your lives! -Vampires!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:10.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,父親\N{\rENG}Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:53.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,一年後-巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.32,0:07:58.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,懸賞范海辛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:08:00.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,兩千法朗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:28.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rENG}Evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:32.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,你的肉很硬  一定很難消化\N{\rENG}You're a big one. You'll be hard to digest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.48,0:09:36.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,那真是難為你了\N{\rENG}I'd hate to be such a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:46.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,我在倫敦沒逮到你\N{\rENG}I missed you in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:50.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,才怪 你射了我一槍\N{\rENG}No, you bloody did not! You got me good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:52.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,變身怪醫  聖靈騎士下令抓你\N{\rENG}Dr. Jekyll, you're wanted by the Knights of the Holy Order...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:54.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,我現在是海德巨人\N{\rENG}It's Mr. Hyde now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.31,0:09:57.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,你殺了十二男、六女…\N{\rENG}...for the murder of 12 men, six women, four--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:10:02.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,四個小孩、三頭山羊 還有一窩子的雞\N{\rENG}...children, three goats, and a rather nasty massacre of poultry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:06.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,你就是鼎鼎大名的范海辛\N{\rENG}So you're the great Van Helsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:09.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,你是喪心病狂的殺人狂\N{\rENG}And you're a deranged psychopath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.19,0:10:17.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,每個人都有點小毛病\N{\rENG}We all have our little problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:21.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的上司要我活捉你\N{\rENG}My superiors would like for me to take you alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:24.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,把你變回正常人\N{\rENG}so that they may extricate your better half.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:27.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們想得美\N{\rENG}I bet they bloody would.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:31.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,我只想宰了你省得麻煩\N{\rENG}Personally, I'd rather just kill you and call it a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:33.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,你自己看著辦\N{\rENG}But let's make it your decision, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:35.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,儘管上吧!\N{\rENG}Do let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:59.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,我來也\N{\rENG}Here I come...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:02.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,領死吧!\N{\rENG}ready or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:07.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,大笨鐘\N{\rENG}The bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.54,0:11:38.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,不  不\N{\rENG}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.58,0:11:42.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,這一定超痛的\N{\rENG}I'll bet that's upsetting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:55.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,巴黎夜景超美的\N{\rENG}Paris!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:01.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,給我過來\N{\rENG}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:08.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,這兒的景觀更贊\N{\rENG}I think you'll find the view over here rather spectacular.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:16.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,很高興認識你  拜了\N{\rENG}It's been a pleasure knowing you. Au revoir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:38.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,不  不要\N{\rENG}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:47.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,該我了\N{\rENG}My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:14.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,安息吧!\N{\rENG}May he rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:32.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,范海辛\N{\rENG}Van Helsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:36.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,你這殺人狂\N{\rENG}You murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.70,0:13:47.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,羅馬-梵蒂岡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:04.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,原諒我  天父  我…\N{\rENG}Bless me, Father, for I have--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:07.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,你犯了罪  我知道\N{\rENG}Sinned. Yes, I know. You're very good at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:10.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,你砸爛了聖母院的玫瑰窗\N{\rENG}You shattered the Rose Window.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:13.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,那是海德巨人幹的好事\N{\rENG}Not to split hairs, sir, but Mr. Hyde did the shattering.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:17.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,六百年的古物毀於一旦\N{\rENG}13th century. Over 600 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:21.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,-我真想把你打下地獄 -正好讓我休個假\N{\rENG}-I wish you a week in hell for that. -lt would be a nice reprieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:25.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,別誤解我的意思 你斬妖除魔的功力一流\N{\rENG}Don't get me wrong. Your results are unquestionable...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:28.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,只是你樹大招風\N{\rENG}but your methods attract far too much attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:31.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,你居然被懸賞通緝 我們很生氣\N{\rENG}"Wanted" posters? We are not pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:34.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,你以為我愛當頭號通緝犯嗎?\N{\rENG}Do you think I like being the most wanted man in Europe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.42,0:14:36.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們為何不幫我想辦法?\N{\rENG}Why don't you and the Order do something about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:39.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,因為我們不存在\N{\rENG}Because we do not exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:41.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,我也一樣\N{\rENG}Well, then neither do l.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:48.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,當年你半死不活出現在教堂\N{\rENG}When we found you crawling up the steps of this church, half-dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:52.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,神派你來替他斬妖除魔\N{\rENG}it was clear to all of us that you had been sent to do God's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:55.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,-他幹嘛不自己來? -不准褻瀆上帝\N{\rENG}-Why can't he do it himself? -Don't blaspheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.11,0:14:59.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,你就是這樣才會失去記憶\N{\rENG}You already lost your memory as a penance for past sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.51,0:15:01.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,你想恢復記憶…\N{\rENG}If you wish to recover it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:04.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,就要奉命行事\N{\rENG}I suggest you continue to heed the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:08.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒有我們  黑暗就會籠罩世界\N{\rENG}Without us, the world would be in darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:12.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,統治者和帝王都不可靠\N{\rENG}Governments and empires come and go...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:16.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,只有我們才能捍衛人類世界…\N{\rENG}but we have kept mankind safe since time immemorial.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.09,0:15:19.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,抵抗邪惡力量\N{\rENG}We are the last defense against evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:23.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,世人都不知曉的可怕惡魔\N{\rENG}An evil that the rest of mankind has no idea even exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:28.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,對你來說它們只是怪物\N{\rENG}To you, these monsters are just evil beings to be vanquished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:31.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,我卻必須承受…\N{\rENG}I'm the one standing there when they die...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:33.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,殺戮的後果\N{\rENG}and become the men they once were.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,0:15:37.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是為了試探你的信仰\N{\rENG}For you, my good son, this is all a test of faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:41.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,你要遠赴東方\N{\rENG}And now, we need you to go to the East.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.72,0:15:44.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,前往羅馬尼亞邊陲\N{\rENG}To the far side of Romania.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:46.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,一個妖孽橫行的…\N{\rENG}An accursed land...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:49.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,禁忌之地\N{\rENG}terrorized by all sorts of nightmarish creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.93,0:15:53.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,吸血鬼德古拉伯爵的領地\N{\rENG}Lorded over by a certain Count Dracula.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:56.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 德古拉? - 對\N{\rENG}- Dracula? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:59.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,前所未有的強勁對手\N{\rENG}You've never faced one like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.94,0:16:03.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,450年前…\N{\rENG}Our story begins 450 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:07.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,一名德蘭斯斐尼亞騎士維拉瑞斯\N{\rENG}when a Transylvanian knight named Valerious the Elder...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.24,0:16:10.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,向上帝保證要消滅吸血鬼…\N{\rENG}promised God that his family would never rest nor enter heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:14.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,否則他的家族將不能上天堂\N{\rENG}until they vanquished Dracula from their land.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.42,0:16:16.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們失敗了\N{\rENG}They have not succeeded...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:19.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,家族香火也快斷絕\N{\rENG}and they are running out of family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:24.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,吉普賽王包瑞斯維拉瑞斯\N{\rENG}His descendant Boris Valerious, King of the Gypsies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:27.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,他一年前消失無蹤\N{\rENG}He disappeared almost 12 months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:34.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,他的獨子威肯王子 還有他的女兒安娜公主\N{\rENG}His only son, Prince Velkan, and his daughter, Princess Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:37.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,在消滅德古拉前他們若遭到不測\N{\rENG}If the two of them are killed before Dracula is vanquished...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:39.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,那九代的祖先都…\N{\rENG}nine generations of their family...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:42.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,無法進入天堂\N{\rENG}will never enter the gates of St. Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:44.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,這家族四百年來…\N{\rENG}For more than four centuries...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:47.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,為了對抗邪惡\N{\rENG}this family has defended our left flank.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.79,0:16:49.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,付出寶貴的生命\N{\rENG}They gave their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:53.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們不能讓他們下地獄\N{\rENG}We cannot let them slip into purgatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:55.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,所以你才派我下地獄\N{\rENG}So you're sending me into hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,可以這麼說\N{\rENG}In a manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.17,0:17:06.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,維拉瑞斯四百年前留下這卷軸\N{\rENG}Valerious the Elder left this here 400 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:08.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,不知道用途\N{\rENG}We don't know its purpose...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:11.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,但一定很重要\N{\rENG}but he would not have left it lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:13.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,拉丁文的意思是…\N{\rENG}The Latin inscription translates as:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.25,0:17:17.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,以天父之命打開此門\N{\rENG}"ln the name of God, open this door."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:20.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,上面有徽章\N{\rENG}There is an insignia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:26.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒錯  跟你的戒指一樣\N{\rENG}Yes, it matches your ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:32.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,你會在那兒解開你的身世之謎\N{\rENG}I think that in Transylvania you may find the answer you seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.94,0:17:41.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,快點、快點\N{\rENG}Faster, please. Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:47.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,就快好了\N{\rENG}Getting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:48.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 卡爾 - 你來了\N{\rENG}- Carl! - There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:51.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,你有沒有活捉變身怪醫? 還是你殺了他?\N{\rENG}Did you bring Mr. Hyde back, or did you kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:55.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,你殺了他  難怪他們會不爽\N{\rENG}You killed him, didn't you? That's why they get so annoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.02,0:17:58.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們可沒叫你帶一具屍體回來\N{\rENG}When they ask you to bring someone back, they don't mean as a corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:00.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,你也心情不好\N{\rENG}All right, you're in a mood. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:02.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,我有東西保證能讓你開心\N{\rENG}I have some things that'll put the bit back in your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:05.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,要鑄劍還不簡單\N{\rENG}Any idiot can make a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.70,0:18:07.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,抱歉  神父\N{\rENG}Sorry, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:09.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 來吧  卡爾 - 拿去\N{\rENG}- Come along, Carl. - Here, take this:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,0:18:14.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,大蒜、聖水…\N{\rENG}Rings of garlic, holy water...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.21,0:18:19.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,銀樁、鎮邪十字架\N{\rENG}silver stake, crucifix.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.21,0:18:24.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,這麼炫的武器我也要\N{\rENG}Why can't I have one of those?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:27.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,你沒殺過吸血鬼  對吧?\N{\rENG}You've never gone after vampires before now, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:29.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,吸血鬼跟其它妖魔鬼怪一樣\N{\rENG}Vampires, gargoyles, warlocks, they're all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:32.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 全都該死 - 不  他們不一樣\N{\rENG}- Best when cooked well. - No, they're not all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:35.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,吸血鬼跟惡鬼不同 連我阿嬤都殺得了惡鬼\N{\rENG}A vampire is nothing like a warlock. My granny could kill a warlock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:37.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,你連大門都不出\N{\rENG}Carl, you've never even been out of the abbey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:40.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你怎麼知道吸血鬼的事? - 我博學多聞呀!\N{\rENG}- How do you know about vampires? - I read.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:43.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是新玩意\N{\rENG}Here's something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:46.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,硝酸甘油\N{\rENG}Glycerin 48.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:53.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\rENG}Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:55.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,你有毛病嗎?\N{\rENG}What in Allah's name is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:58.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們都嫉妒我\N{\rENG}The air around here is thick with envy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:19:02.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是我的新發明 瓦斯推動的…\N{\rENG}This is my latest invention. It's gas-propelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.52,0:19:04.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,超強除魔火箭弓\N{\rENG}Capable of catapulting arrows in rapid succession at tremendous velocity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:08.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,只要扣下扳機就行\N{\rENG}Just pull the trigger and hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.39,0:19:11.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,聽說德蘭斯斐尼亞群魔亂舞\N{\rENG}I've heard the stories from Transylvania.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:14.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,你需要這個 這是天才的精心傑作\N{\rENG}Trust me, you'll need this. A work of certifiable genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:17.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你真會自賣自誇 - 不是我自誇喲!\N{\rENG}- lf you don't say so yourself. - No, I did say so myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:19.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,我是真的多才多藝\N{\rENG}I'm a veritable cornucopia of talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.77,0:19:21.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,這也是你發明的?\N{\rENG}Did you invent this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.37,0:19:23.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,這玩意我研究了十二年\N{\rENG}I've been working on that for 12 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.31,0:19:25.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,維蘇威火山的熔漿\N{\rENG}It's compressed magma from Mt. Vesuvius...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:27.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,和來自戈壁沙漠的純鹼\N{\rENG}with pure alkaline from the Gobi Desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:29.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 獨一無二 - 拿來幹嘛?\N{\rENG}- It's one of a kind. - What's it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.65,0:19:32.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,不曉得  不過一定會派上用場\N{\rENG}I don't know, but I'm sure it'll come in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.32,0:19:34.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,你研究了十二年都還沒搞懂?\N{\rENG}Twelve years, and you don't know what it does?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:37.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,我只是不知道它的用途\N{\rENG}I didn't say that. I said I didn't know what it's for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:39.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,它能製造…\N{\rENG}What it does is to create a light source...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:41.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,跟太陽一樣強的光亮\N{\rENG}equal to the intensity of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.43,0:19:43.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,用來做什麼?\N{\rENG}This will come in handy how?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:45.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,不曉得 把敵人的眼睛閃瞎\N{\rENG}I don't know. You can blind your enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:47.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,或是烤BBQ\N{\rENG}Charbroil a herd of charging wildebeest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:49.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,你自己動動腦筋嘛!\N{\rENG}Use your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:52.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不用動腦筋  你要跟我來\N{\rENG}No, I'm gonna use yours. That's why you're coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:54.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我才不幹咧! - 你罵了髒話\N{\rENG}- Holy hell be damned I am! - You cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.74,0:19:56.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,罵得很爛\N{\rENG}Not very well,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:19:58.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,你是和尚  不該罵髒話\N{\rENG}but you're a monk. You shouldn't curse at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.08,0:20:01.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,我只是修道士  愛罵就罵\N{\rENG}Actually, I'm still just a friar. I can curse all I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:02.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,該死!\N{\rENG}damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:06.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,主教命令你幫助我\N{\rENG}The Cardinal has ordered you to keep me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.32,0:20:10.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 活得越久越好 - 我不搞這一套啦!\N{\rENG}- For as long as possible. - But I'm not a field man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:11.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,范海辛\N{\rENG}Van Helsing
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.82,0:20:14.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,我真的不想去德蘭斯斐尼亞\N{\rENG}I don't want to go to Transylvania.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:56.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,來吧!\N{\rENG}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:21:00.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,德古拉派你來一定有原因\N{\rENG}Dracula unleashed you for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.19,0:21:24.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,快把我拉上去\N{\rENG}Pull me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.73,0:21:26.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,卡住了!\N{\rENG}It's stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.44,0:21:37.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 不  安娜  它會吃了你 - 我哥哥有危險\N{\rENG}- No, Anna, it will kill you! - That's my brother out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.41,0:21:42.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,把繩子切斷\N{\rENG}Cut the rope! Cut it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.39,0:21:57.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,威肯!\N{\rENG}Velkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:10.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,快去拿我的槍\N{\rENG}My gun! Find my gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.44,0:22:13.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,快去  一定要用銀彈\N{\rENG}Find Velkan's gun. It has to be the silver bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.58,0:22:19.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,安娜!快點!\N{\rENG}Anna, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.09,0:22:23.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,讓開!\N{\rENG}Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.06,0:22:26.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,安娜!小心!\N{\rENG}Anna, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.99,0:22:30.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,快跑!\N{\rENG}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.29,0:23:01.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,威肯\N{\rENG}Velkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:08.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,神啊!\N{\rENG}God...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.10,0:23:11.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,請幫助我們\N{\rENG}help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.24,0:24:26.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你到底還記得些什麼? - 卡爾  我現在不想談\N{\rENG}- So, what do you remember? - Not now, Carl.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.38,0:24:28.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,你一定記得些什麼\N{\rENG}There must be something.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.85,0:24:31.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,我記得在馬薩達對抗過羅馬大軍\N{\rENG}I remember fighting the Romans at Masada.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.02,0:24:34.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 那是千年前的事! - 是你要問的\N{\rENG}- That was in 73 A.D. - You asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.49,0:24:39.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們來這裡做什麼?\N{\rENG}What are we doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.16,0:24:41.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,幹嘛非得殺死吸血鬼德古拉?\N{\rENG}Why is it so important to kill this Dracula, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.56,0:24:44.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 因為他是惡魔之子 - 除此之外呢?\N{\rENG}- Because he's the son of the Devil. - I mean, besides that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.66,0:24:48.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,殺了他  他的徒子徒孫也會死\N{\rENG}If we kill him, anything bitten or created by him will also die.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.07,0:24:49.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,還有咧?\N{\rENG}I mean, besides that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.17,0:24:52.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,歡迎來到德蘭斯斐尼亞\N{\rENG}Welcome to Transylvania.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.65,0:25:06.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你總是這麼顧人怨嗎? - 差不多\N{\rENG}- ls it always like this? - Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.89,0:25:09.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們  轉過來\N{\rENG}You, turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.36,0:25:15.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 給我看看 - 為什麼?\N{\rENG}- Let me see your faces. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.59,0:25:17.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們不信任陌生人\N{\rENG}Because we don't trust strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.96,0:25:20.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,陌生人不受歡迎\N{\rENG}Strangers don't last long here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.66,0:25:23.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,長170公分  寬70公分\N{\rENG}5'7" by 2'3".
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.84,0:25:27.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,兩位  交出武器\N{\rENG}Gentlemen, you will now be disarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.41,0:25:30.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,試試看\N{\rENG}You can try.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.71,0:25:36.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,你敢不聽我的話?\N{\rENG}You refuse to obey our laws?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.08,0:25:39.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我誰都不甩 - 好吧!\N{\rENG}- The laws of men mean little to me. - Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.88,0:25:41.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,殺了他們\N{\rENG}Kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.08,0:25:44.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我是來幫你的 - 我不需要幫忙\N{\rENG}- I'm here to help you. - I don't need any help.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.02,0:25:45.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,真的嗎?\N{\rENG}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.14,0:26:04.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,快進去!\N{\rENG}Everybody inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.44,0:26:06.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,快把小孩子藏起來!\N{\rENG}Hide the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.74,0:26:35.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,留下來\N{\rENG}Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.57,0:26:38.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,你才留下來  她們想殺我\N{\rENG}You stay here. They're trying to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.85,0:26:47.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 蜜西卡  殺了陌生人 - 我很樂意\N{\rENG}- Marishka, kill the stranger. - Love to.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.06,0:26:54.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,快跑!\N{\rENG}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.74,0:27:07.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,卡爾  十字弓沒有用\N{\rENG}Carl, it's not working.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.30,0:27:09.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,瞄準她們的心臟\N{\rENG}Try aiming at their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.68,0:27:52.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,她們怕太陽\N{\rENG}It's the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.61,0:28:55.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,范海辛?\N{\rENG}Van Helsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.48,0:29:03.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,你想飛嗎?\N{\rENG}Do you like to fly, Anna?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.98,0:30:00.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,哈羅  安娜\N{\rENG}Hello, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.92,0:30:08.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,你好嗎? 艾莉拉\N{\rENG}Nice to see you, too, Aleera.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.46,0:30:54.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,我上輩子欠你一命嗎?\N{\rENG}Did I do something to you in a past life?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.83,0:30:57.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,少裝蒜\N{\rENG}Don't play coy with me, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.60,0:31:04.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,其實你想什麼我很清楚\N{\rENG}I know what lurks in your lusting heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.41,0:31:06.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,你自己要小心點\N{\rENG}I hope you have a heart, Aleera...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.94,0:31:10.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,有一天我會殺了你\N{\rENG}because someday I'm going to drive a stake through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.89,0:31:23.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,這玩意很有用\N{\rENG}This should do the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.06,0:31:25.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,聖水\N{\rENG}Holy water!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.74,0:31:35.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,別浪費時間  幹掉他\N{\rENG}Stop your teasing, Marishka, and finish him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.84,0:31:41.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,殺了他有點可惜\N{\rENG}Too bad. So sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.18,0:31:43.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,教堂聖水\N{\rENG}The church!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.53,0:31:57.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,三十歲\N{\rENG}Thirty years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.83,0:31:59.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,年紀正好\N{\rENG}Perfectly aged.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.30,0:32:02.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,親愛的安娜\N{\rENG}Hello, Anna, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.41,0:32:16.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,維拉瑞斯家族最後成員\N{\rENG}The last of the Valerious.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.51,0:32:54.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,我要狂吸她的鮮血\N{\rENG}I can feel fresh blood rushing through her veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.15,0:32:57.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,她來了\N{\rENG}Here she comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.96,0:33:05.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,我要吸第一口\N{\rENG}I want first bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.74,0:34:27.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 他殺死吸血鬼新娘 - 他殺死蜜西卡\N{\rENG}- He killed a bride! - He killed Marishka!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.08,0:34:34.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,你殺了蜜西卡!\N{\rENG}You killed Marishka!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.68,0:34:37.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你殺了吸血鬼! - 這樣不好嗎?\N{\rENG}- You killed a vampire! - But isn't that a good thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.85,0:34:40.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,吸血鬼不得已才吸人血\N{\rENG}Vampires only kill what they need to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.86,0:34:43.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,一個月最多殺一、兩人\N{\rENG}One or two people a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.46,0:34:46.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,現在他們會大開殺戒\N{\rENG}Now they will kill for revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.43,0:34:53.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你粉受歡迎耶 - 我是萬人迷\N{\rENG}- Are you always this popular? - Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.47,0:34:57.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,你的墓碑上要刻什麼名字?\N{\rENG}So what name, my good sir, do I carve on your gravestone?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.97,0:35:00.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,他叫范海辛\N{\rENG}His name is Van Helsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.75,0:35:09.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,你真是臭名遠播\N{\rENG}Your reputation precedes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.26,0:35:17.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,下次跟緊點  你死了就沒用\N{\rENG}Next time stay close. You're no good to me dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.16,0:35:21.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,你挺帶種的嘛!\N{\rENG}Well, I'll say this for you. You've got courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.70,0:35:25.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,他是百年來擒殺吸血鬼第一人\N{\rENG}He's the first one to kill a vampire in over 100 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.84,0:35:28.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,絕對有資格喝一杯\N{\rENG}I'd say that's earned him a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.11,0:35:37.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,蜜西卡\N{\rENG}Marishka!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.59,0:35:47.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們怎麼不饒過我們?\N{\rENG}Why can't they just leave us alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.09,0:35:51.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們從不濫殺無辜\N{\rENG}We never kill more than our fill and less than our share.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.49,0:35:53.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們辦得到嗎?\N{\rENG}Can they say the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.23,0:35:56.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,我叫你們…\N{\rENG}Did I not stress how important it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.93,0:35:59.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,幹掉魏氏家族\N{\rENG}to be finished with Anna Valerious...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.80,0:36:03.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們就快實現夢想了\N{\rENG}before she destroys what we are trying to create?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.44,0:36:06.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 蜜西卡死了 - 主人\N{\rENG}- We lost Marishka. - Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.61,0:36:10.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,親愛的  別擔心\N{\rENG}There, there, my darlings. Do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.48,0:36:13.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我會找另一個新娘 - 什麼?\N{\rENG}- I shall find another bride. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.32,0:36:18.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你嫌棄我們嗎? - 你好沒良心哦!\N{\rENG}- Do we mean so little to you? - Have you no heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.12,0:36:23.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,我沒有良心  也沒有愛\N{\rENG}No, I have no heart! I feel no love!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.86,0:36:25.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒有恐懼\N{\rENG}Nor fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.46,0:36:28.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒有喜悅\N{\rENG}nor joy...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.33,0:36:31.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,更沒有悲傷\N{\rENG}nor sorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.74,0:36:35.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,我也沒有感覺\N{\rENG}I am hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.88,0:36:42.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,但是我有不死之身\N{\rENG}And I will live forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.91,0:36:46.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 主人 - 其實沒這麼糟\N{\rENG}- My Lord. - lt is not so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.32,0:36:51.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,我與全世界為敵\N{\rENG}I am at war with the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.89,0:36:55.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,還有世上的每種生物\N{\rENG}and every living soul in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.23,0:36:58.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,大戰即將展開\N{\rENG}But soon the final battle will begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.90,0:37:01.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,我要摸清敵人的底細\N{\rENG}I must go and find out who our new visitor is.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.47,0:37:10.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,咱們要吸他的血當餐前酒\N{\rENG}You will have to make a little aperitif out of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.41,0:37:13.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不能讓他壞了我們的大事\N{\rENG}We are much too close to success to be interrupted now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.41,0:37:17.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 不 - 上次的實驗失敗\N{\rENG}- No! - The last experiment was a failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.18,0:37:21.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,求求你別再嘗試\N{\rENG}Please, say you will not try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.48,0:37:26.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,我無法承受再失敗的痛苦\N{\rENG}My heart could not bear the sorrow if we fail again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.00,0:37:37.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,過來\N{\rENG}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.97,0:37:41.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,別害怕\N{\rENG}Do not fear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.24,0:37:43.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,世人都畏懼我\N{\rENG}Everybody else fears me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.01,0:37:46.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的新娘不必怕我\N{\rENG}Not my brides.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.61,0:37:52.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,伊果\N{\rENG}lgor.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.85,0:37:55.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,是  主人\N{\rENG}Yes, master.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.69,0:37:58.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,你為何虐待這可憐蟲?\N{\rENG}Why do you torment that thing so?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.86,0:38:00.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,人性本惡呀!\N{\rENG}It's what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.62,0:38:03.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,你要記住  己所不欲…\N{\rENG}Remember, lgor, "Do unto others...."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.33,0:38:07.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,必施於人\N{\rENG}Before they do unto me, master.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.00,0:38:11.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,回去吧!\N{\rENG}Now go, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.37,0:38:13.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,全都給我去法蘭肯斯坦堡\N{\rENG}To Castle Frankenstein!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.20,0:38:18.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,對  我們再試一次\N{\rENG}Yes, we will try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.55,0:38:25.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你們是怎麼來的? - 走海路\N{\rENG}- So, how did you get here? - We came by sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.38,0:38:27.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 真的?海路? - 是的\N{\rENG}- Really? The sea? - Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.45,0:38:30.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 亞得里亞海? - 吸血鬼住在哪裡?\N{\rENG}- The Adriatic Sea? - Where do I find Dracula?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.65,0:38:33.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,四世紀前他住在這兒\N{\rENG}He used to live in this very house four centuries ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.72,0:38:35.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,現在沒人知道他的巢穴\N{\rENG}No one knows where he lives now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.76,0:38:37.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,我父親總是盯著那幅畫…\N{\rENG}Father would stare at that painting for hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.93,0:38:39.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,找答案\N{\rENG}Iooking for Dracula's lair.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.70,0:38:42.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你為什麼要來? - 我能幫助你\N{\rENG}- So that's why you've come? - I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.43,0:38:45.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 誰也幫不了我 - 我可以試試\N{\rENG}- No one can help me. - I can try.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.77,0:38:49.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,我全家都死光光了\N{\rENG}You can die trying. All of my family has.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.11,0:38:51.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我能保護自己 - 才怪\N{\rENG}- I can handle this myself. - So I noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.81,0:38:54.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,這次吸血鬼在白天出擊\N{\rENG}The vampires attacked in daylight. They never do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.51,0:38:56.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,我沒有準備  下次不會了\N{\rENG}I was unprepared. It won't happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.98,0:38:58.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們為什麼白天出擊?\N{\rENG}So why did they attack in daylight?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.85,0:39:01.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,好讓我措手不及\N{\rENG}Clearly they wanted to catch me off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.22,0:39:03.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們想除掉我全家\N{\rENG}They seem almost desperate to finish off my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.65,0:39:07.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 為什麼要在現在? - 你很愛問耶\N{\rENG}- Why is that? Why now? - You ask a lot of questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.12,0:39:08.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,我通常只會問…\N{\rENG}Usually I ask only two:
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.59,0:39:10.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,對手是誰? 怎麼殺他?\N{\rENG}What are we dealing with? How do I kill it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.49,0:39:14.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,父親終其一生在尋找答案\N{\rENG}My father spent most of his life looking for answers year after year.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.26,0:39:17.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,他翻遍了高塔的文獻\N{\rENG}Tearing through the tower, combing through the family archives.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.40,0:39:19.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 卡爾  從高塔找起 - 好的\N{\rENG}- Carl, the tower. Start there. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.84,0:39:23.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,你不能比吸血鬼先死\N{\rENG}The only way to save your family is to stay alive till Dracula's killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.37,0:39:27.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,除了我誰能殺他? 除了我誰有這勇氣?\N{\rENG}And who will kill him if not me? Who will show courage if not me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.04,0:39:29.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,你一個人勢單力薄\N{\rENG}Go alone and you'll be outmanned and outpositioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.61,0:39:31.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,晚上也看不到他\N{\rENG}And you can't see in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.65,0:39:34.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們明天一早再獵殺他\N{\rENG}In the morning, we will hunt him...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.82,0:39:37.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,一起行動\N{\rENG}but we'll do it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.99,0:39:46.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,有人說你是殺人狂\N{\rENG}Some say you're a murderer, Mr. Van Helsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.36,0:39:50.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,有人說你是聖人 你到底是什麼?\N{\rENG}Others say you're a holy man. Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.57,0:39:56.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,都是吧!\N{\rENG}It's a bit of both, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.14,0:40:02.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我答應請你喝一杯 - 沒錯\N{\rENG}- I promised you a drink. - Yes, you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.08,0:40:05.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,酒吧在那兒  請自便\N{\rENG}The bar is down the hall. Help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.82,0:40:09.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,失陪了  我要去殺吸血鬼\N{\rENG}As for me, I'm going to finish this once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.59,0:40:11.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,你不該單獨背負這重擔\N{\rENG}Sorry you've to carry this burden alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.89,0:40:14.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是我一個人的責任\N{\rENG}On the contrary, I would wish for it no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.19,0:40:16.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,我為你父兄的死感到遺憾\N{\rENG}I'm sorry about your father and brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.03,0:40:17.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,我會再見到他們\N{\rENG}I will see them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.66,0:40:20.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們對死很看得開\N{\rENG}We Transylvanians always look on the brighter side of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.53,0:40:25.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你不怕死 - 對  你只是看不透\N{\rENG}- There's a brighter side of death? - Yes. It's just harder to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.84,0:40:34.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,很對不起\N{\rENG}I'm sorry about that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.02,0:40:48.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,該死的范海辛\N{\rENG}Van Helsing!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.54,0:41:01.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,范海辛?\N{\rENG}Van Helsing?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.72,0:43:28.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 威肯? - 安娜\N{\rENG}- Velkan? - Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.49,0:43:31.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,老天  你還活著\N{\rENG}Oh, my God, you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.66,0:43:35.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的時間不多\N{\rENG}No. Anna, I only have a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.56,0:43:37.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 剛才有一隻狼… - 別管了\N{\rENG}- But there's a werewolf-- - Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.93,0:43:40.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,我知道德古拉的秘密…\N{\rENG}I know Dracula's secret. He has a....
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.90,0:43:47.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 威肯? - 求求你\N{\rENG}- Velkan? - Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.64,0:43:50.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,不!\N{\rENG}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.00,0:44:19.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,快跑\N{\rENG}Run, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.22,0:44:39.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,安娜\N{\rENG}Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.36,0:44:47.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧?\N{\rENG}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.75,0:45:05.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,怎麼會有狗臭味?\N{\rENG}Why does it smell like wet dog in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.38,0:45:06.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,狼人!\N{\rENG}Werewolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.55,0:45:08.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒錯  你需要銀彈\N{\rENG}Right. You'll be needing silver bullets, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.62,0:45:10.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,好樣的\N{\rENG}Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.77,0:46:00.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,誰在獵捕誰呀?\N{\rENG}Who's hunting whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.31,0:46:13.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,夜色真美 我睡這具棺材太窄了\N{\rENG}Nice night. This is a bit tight for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.25,0:46:17.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,你睡正好\N{\rENG}But for you it's a perfect fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.62,0:46:20.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,真巧\N{\rENG}What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.26,0:46:23.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,你沒被狼人吃掉\N{\rENG}I see the wolf man hasn't killed you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.69,0:46:25.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,他很想\N{\rENG}Don't worry, he's getting to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.63,0:46:28.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你好像不怕他 - 我對他不造成威脅\N{\rENG}- You don't seem bothered. - I'm no threat to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.73,0:46:31.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,我負責替他收拾殘局\N{\rENG}I'm just the one who cleans up after him...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.00,0:46:33.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,你了嗎?\N{\rENG}if you get my meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.77,0:46:35.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,這麼晚還在挖墳?\N{\rENG}Little late to be digging graves, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.94,0:46:38.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,墳墓永遠挖不完\N{\rENG}Never too late to dig graves.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.81,0:46:43.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,誰曉得幾時又會死人\N{\rENG}You never know when you'll need a fresh one.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.71,0:46:50.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,抱歉 本性難移\N{\rENG}Oh, sorry. It's just my nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.77,0:47:09.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 讓開 - 不\N{\rENG}- Move! - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.34,0:47:16.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 為什麼? - 你會掐死我!\N{\rENG}- Why? - You're choking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.51,0:47:21.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 快說! - 我不能讓別人知道…\N{\rENG}- Give me a reason not to. - I can't. If people knew....
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.62,0:47:27.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,他不是你哥哥了\N{\rENG}He's not your brother anymore, Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.07,0:47:31.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你已經知道了?  - 是的\N{\rENG}- You knew?  -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.76,0:47:36.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,在我阻止你之前或之後?\N{\rENG}Before or after I stopped you from shooting him?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.17,0:47:37.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,之前\N{\rENG}Before.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.27,0:47:38.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,你還是向他下手\N{\rENG}And still you tried to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.70,0:47:40.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,他是狼人! 他會吃人!\N{\rENG}He's a werewolf! He's gonna kill people!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.30,0:47:42.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,他也不願意! 那不是他的錯!\N{\rENG}He can't help it! It's not his fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.10,0:47:43.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,但是他還是會吃人!\N{\rENG}I know, but he'll do it anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.54,0:47:46.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,你不懂得寬恕嗎?\N{\rENG}Do you understand forgiveness?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.01,0:47:48.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,我會請上帝寬恕他們\N{\rENG}Yes. I ask for it often.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.91,0:47:53.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,聽說德古拉有解藥\N{\rENG}They say Dracula has a cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.02,0:47:54.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,只要有任何的可能性…\N{\rENG}If there's a chance I can save my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.98,0:47:56.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我要找來救我哥 - 不\N{\rENG}- I'm going after it. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.45,0:47:59.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我要找到德古拉 - 我要找到我哥\N{\rENG}- I need to find Dracula. - And I need to find my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.22,0:48:03.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,他是我唯一的家人\N{\rENG}He gave his life for me. He's the only family I have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.99,0:48:07.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,我比誰都更痛恨德古拉\N{\rENG}I despise Dracula more than you can ever imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.63,0:48:11.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,他害我孤零零一個人在世上\N{\rENG}He has taken everything from me, leaving me alone in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.68,0:48:30.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,擁有痛失親人的記憶…\N{\rENG}To have memories of those you loved and lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.35,0:48:33.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,比失去記憶更難過\N{\rENG}is perhaps harder than to have no memories at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.72,0:48:37.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,好吧!\N{\rENG}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.36,0:48:41.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們去找你哥哥\N{\rENG}We'll look for your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.23,0:49:12.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 伊果 - 是  主人\N{\rENG}- lgor. - Yes, master.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.00,0:49:16.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 好了沒? - 就快好了\N{\rENG}- How long before we are ready? - Soon, master. Very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.03,0:49:20.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,可惜你把博士殺死了\N{\rENG}It is difficult without the good doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.64,0:49:23.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,不過矮靈族很有用\N{\rENG}but the Dwergi, they are doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.74,0:49:25.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rENG}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.38,0:49:27.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,那就好\N{\rENG}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.41,0:49:34.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是我的個人恩怨 我要替我全家報仇雪恨\N{\rENG}For me, this is all personal. It's all about family and honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.92,0:49:38.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,你為什麼要斬妖除魔? 你能得到什麼?\N{\rENG}Why do you do it, this job of yours? What do you hope to get out of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.72,0:49:41.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,也許是為了尋找自我\N{\rENG}I don't know. Maybe some self-realization.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.36,0:49:45.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,你到現在得到什麼?\N{\rENG}What have you got out of it so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.69,0:49:47.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,無止盡的惡夢\N{\rENG}Nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.67,0:49:52.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,狼人尚未被詛咒完全控制之前…\N{\rENG}Werewolves only shed before the first full moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.67,0:49:54.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,會在第一次月圓之前開始脫皮\N{\rENG}Before the curse has completely consumed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.95,0:50:09.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 這是哪裡? - 法蘭肯斯坦堡\N{\rENG}- What is this place? - Castle Frankenstein.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.22,0:50:11.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,應該沒人在\N{\rENG}But it should be abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.15,0:50:12.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不懂\N{\rENG}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.39,0:50:14.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,這兒的主人一年前遇害\N{\rENG}The man who lived here was killed a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.89,0:50:17.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 他是盜墓者 - 一年前\N{\rENG}- A grave robber, among other things. - A year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.66,0:50:20.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,你父親一年前失蹤\N{\rENG}It was just after that your father went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.16,0:50:24.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,他為了抓吸血鬼 準備去海邊\N{\rENG}Yes. He was looking for Dracula. He was on his way to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.53,0:50:27.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,我沒見過大海\N{\rENG}I have never been to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.74,0:50:35.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,一定很美\N{\rENG}I'll bet it's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.73,0:50:56.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,狼人一碰到月圓就抓狂\N{\rENG}Werewolves are such a nuisance during their first full moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.70,0:50:59.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,難以控制\N{\rENG}So hard to control.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.26,0:51:25.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,我派你…\N{\rENG}I send you on a simple errand...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.43,0:51:28.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,去摸清敵人的底細\N{\rENG}to find out who our new visitor is...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.50,0:51:32.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,你卻去找老妹聊天\N{\rENG}and you have to stop for a little chat with your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.07,0:51:36.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,別傷害她 她不知道你的秘密\N{\rENG}Leave her out of this, Count. She doesn't know your secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.11,0:51:38.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,我死也不會說\N{\rENG}And I am soon to take it to my grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.64,0:51:43.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,你不能死  你對我還有用\N{\rENG}Don't wish for death so quickly. I intend for you to be quite useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.38,0:51:45.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,我死也不會幫你\N{\rENG}I would rather die than help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.21,0:51:48.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,別傻了  說這種話一定會掛\N{\rENG}Don't be boring. Everyone who says that dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.38,0:51:50.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,今晚…\N{\rENG}Besides, tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.09,0:51:52.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,一過午夜…\N{\rENG}after the final stroke of midnight...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.05,0:51:55.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,你就必須唯我是從\N{\rENG}you will have no choice but to obey me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.19,0:51:59.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,很眼熟吧?\N{\rENG}Look familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.23,0:52:04.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,父親?\N{\rENG}Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.17,0:52:07.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,不!\N{\rENG}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.10,0:52:08.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,他沒什麼用\N{\rENG}He proved useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.50,0:52:11.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,我希望你變成狼人…\N{\rENG}But I'm hoping, with werewolf venom running through your veins...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.87,0:52:14.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,比較好用\N{\rENG}you will be of greater benefit!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.08,0:52:22.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,我殺不了你  我妹妹一定會\N{\rENG}I may have failed to kill you, Count, but my sister will not.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.49,0:52:31.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,不  不要\N{\rENG}Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.34,0:52:50.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 矮靈族 - 矮靈族?\N{\rENG}- Dwergi. - Dwergi?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.41,0:52:54.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,德古拉的爪牙 刻苦耐勞、兇狠殘暴\N{\rENG}Dracula's servants. Industrious but extremely vicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.08,0:52:55.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,你得先下手為強\N{\rENG}If you get the chance to kill one, do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.98,0:52:59.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 不然就會死得很慘 - 知道了\N{\rENG}- because they'll do worse to you. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.19,0:53:07.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們利用威肯做實驗\N{\rENG}They say they're using my brother in some sort of experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.10,0:53:09.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,我哥還在自我掙扎\N{\rENG}My brother is still battling the sickness within him.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.57,0:53:11.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 他還有一線希望 - 安娜\N{\rENG}- There's still hope. - Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.30,0:53:14.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,他沒有救了\N{\rENG}There is no hope for your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.94,0:53:18.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們得殺了德古拉\N{\rENG}But we can still protect others by killing Dracula.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.35,0:53:27.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,開始吧!\N{\rENG}Let us begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.09,0:53:39.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,抬起來\N{\rENG}No slacking! Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.59,0:53:56.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你見過這東西沒?  - 沒\N{\rENG}- You ever see these things before? - No
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.76,0:53:59.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 是什麼? - 吸血鬼寶寶\N{\rENG}- What do you think they are? - Offspring.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.15,0:54:00.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,什麼?\N{\rENG}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.25,0:54:02.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,他跟三個美女混了四百年耶\N{\rENG}A man with three gorgeous women for 400 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.32,0:54:05.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,吸血鬼是活死人\N{\rENG}Yes, vampires are the walking dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.05,0:54:07.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,後代一出生就死了\N{\rENG}It only makes sense their children are born dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.62,0:54:10.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,他想讓他們復活\N{\rENG}He's obviously trying to bring them to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.36,0:54:17.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,女士優先\N{\rENG}Ladies first.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.86,0:54:45.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們每個月都殺一、兩人\N{\rENG}Dracula and his brides only kill one or two people a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.99,0:54:49.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,這些小吸血鬼活過來就慘了\N{\rENG}If he brings all these things to life....
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.18,0:55:08.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 打開開關 - 是  主人\N{\rENG}- Throw the switches! - Yes, master.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.22,0:55:45.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,你在幹嘛?\N{\rENG}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.35,0:55:47.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,摸清敵人底細\N{\rENG}I want to see what we're up against.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.25,0:56:21.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,原來這就是吸血鬼寶寶\N{\rENG}So this is what you get when vampires mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.35,0:56:44.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,來吧!\N{\rENG}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.18,0:57:20.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們該吸血了 去教他們  快去\N{\rENG}They need to feed. Teach them how. Teach them!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.22,0:57:31.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,向魔鬼祈禱…\N{\rENG}And beg the Devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.49,0:57:35.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,這次他們能活下去\N{\rENG}that this time they stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.64,0:57:47.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 該我上場了 - 等等\N{\rENG}- This is where I come in. - No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.75,0:58:00.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,來領死吧!\N{\rENG}Now that I have your attention....
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.05,0:58:26.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,有意思\N{\rENG}Yes, well, that's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.92,0:58:38.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,慘了  我得警告大家\N{\rENG}That's not good. Must warn somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.01,0:58:56.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,心跳能透露一個人的個性\N{\rENG}I can tell the character of a man by the sound of his heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.15,0:59:00.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,平常人只要看到我…\N{\rENG}Usually when I approach...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.28,0:59:05.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,心跳就會加速\N{\rENG}I can almost dance to the beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.19,0:59:11.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,你的心跳卻很穩定\N{\rENG}Strange that yours is so steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.67,0:59:21.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,快一點!\N{\rENG}Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.31,0:59:26.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,一定要讓空氣充滿電力\N{\rENG}We must keep the atmosphere electrified!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.41,0:59:30.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,加強發電機\N{\rENG}Accelerate the generators!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.51,0:59:33.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,發出電擊\N{\rENG}Power the dynamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.58,0:59:36.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,失去動力了\N{\rENG}We are losing power.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.42,0:59:39.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,這傢伙沒有用\N{\rENG}The human is insufficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.23,0:59:46.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,威肯\N{\rENG}Velkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.61,1:00:01.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\rENG}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.54,1:00:36.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,去吸血吧!乖孩子\N{\rENG}Feed, my darlings! Feed!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.50,1:01:00.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,安息吧!\N{\rENG}May he rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.17,1:01:05.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,你好  蓋布歐\N{\rENG}Hello, Gabriel.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.93,1:02:06.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們不能讓主人絕子絕孫\N{\rENG}We must not lose the master's progeny!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.60,1:02:12.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,這玩意傷不了我\N{\rENG}Is this your silver stake?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.81,1:02:20.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,咱們有多久沒見了? 三、四百年?\N{\rENG}How long has it been? 300, 400 years?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.05,1:02:27.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,你不記得了  對吧?\N{\rENG}You don't remember, do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.36,1:02:32.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,記得什麼?\N{\rENG}Exactly what is it I should be remembering?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.73,1:02:34.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,你是偉大的范海辛\N{\rENG}You are the great Van Helsing.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.73,1:02:38.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,西藏喇嘛親手調教的怪物獵人\N{\rENG}Trained by monks and mullahs from Tibet to lstanbul.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.77,1:02:42.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,受到羅馬教廷的保護\N{\rENG}Protected by Rome herself.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.84,1:02:46.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,但卻跟我一樣被世人唾棄\N{\rENG}But, like me, hunted by all others.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.41,1:02:48.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,聖靈騎士對你瞭若指掌\N{\rENG}The Knights of the Holy Order know all about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.88,1:02:50.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,你當然查過我的底細\N{\rENG}It's no surprise you would know about me.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.71,1:02:53.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,事情沒那麼簡單\N{\rENG}Yes, but it's much more than this.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.45,1:03:02.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,我跟你的交情非淺\N{\rENG}We have such history, you and l, Gabriel.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.83,1:03:11.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,你為什麼會做可怕的噩夢?\N{\rENG}Have you ever wondered why you have such horrible nightmares?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.87,1:03:15.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,夢到古老戰場的慘烈殺戮\N{\rENG}Horrific scenes of ancient battles past.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.84,1:03:21.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,你怎麼會知道?\N{\rENG}How do you know me?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.25,1:03:32.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 威肯 - 安娜\N{\rENG}- Velkan. - Anna.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.35,1:03:34.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,別救我  住手\N{\rENG}No. Don't unstrap me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.42,1:03:38.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,別這麼做  住手\N{\rENG}No, you must not! No! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.43,1:03:40.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,住手 我要救你出去\N{\rENG}Stop it. I'm getting you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.06,1:03:42.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,威肯  沒關係 我帶你回家\N{\rENG}Velkan, it's all right. I'm taking you home.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.97,1:03:53.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,你要我喚起你的記憶?\N{\rENG}So would you like me to refresh your memory a little?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.68,1:03:57.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,說出你幹過的壞事?\N{\rENG}A few details from your sordid past.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.52,1:04:10.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,改天再聊吧!\N{\rENG}Perhaps that is a conversation for another time.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.53,1:04:16.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,讓我重新自我介紹\N{\rENG}Allow me to reintroduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.17,1:04:22.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,我是范斯勞德古拉伯爵\N{\rENG}I am Count Vladislaus Dragulia.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.04,1:04:26.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,1422年出生\N{\rENG}Born 1422.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.71,1:04:31.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,1462年遇害\N{\rENG}Murdered 1462.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.69,1:04:46.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,救命啊!救救我\N{\rENG}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.78,1:05:37.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,咱們待太久了\N{\rENG}I think we've overstayed our welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.93,1:06:26.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 找到小孩了嗎? - 還沒\N{\rENG}- Have you found the children? - Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.86,1:06:33.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 怎麼回事? - 他們掛掉了\N{\rENG}- What happened? - They just died.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.24,1:06:40.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,我該怎麼報答你?\N{\rENG}How can I ever repay you?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.78,1:06:50.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,不行啦!你是和尚耶\N{\rENG}But you can't do that. You are a monk.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.45,1:06:53.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,其實我只是修道士\N{\rENG}Well, actually I'm just a friar.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.76,1:06:59.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,對不起  我們盡了全力\N{\rENG}I am sorry, master. We try and we try...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.29,1:07:04.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,但只有法蘭肯斯坦博士才有辦法\N{\rENG}but I fear we are not so smart as Dr. Frankenstein.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.47,1:07:05.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒錯\N{\rENG}Truly.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.90,1:07:11.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,看來他把復活之鑰帶進棺材\N{\rENG}It would appear the good doctor took the key to life to his grave.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.11,1:07:17.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,找到他們\N{\rENG}Hunt them down.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.25,1:07:22.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,把他們殺了\N{\rENG}Kill them both.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.82,1:07:27.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,銀樁? 十字架?\N{\rENG}A silver stake? A crucifix?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.72,1:07:30.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,你以為我們沒試過嗎?\N{\rENG}What, did you think we haven't tried everything before?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.36,1:07:33.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們無所不用其極\N{\rENG}We've shot him, stabbed him, clubbed him...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.13,1:07:35.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,但是連聖水…\N{\rENG}sprayed him with holy water, staked him through the heart...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.93,1:07:37.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,都殺不了他\N{\rENG}and still he lives! Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.80,1:07:39.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒人知道該怎麼殺他\N{\rENG}No one knows how to kill Dracula.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.73,1:07:43.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,你早說嘛!\N{\rENG}Well, I could have used that information a little earlier.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.67,1:07:45.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,別這樣看我\N{\rENG}Don't give me that look.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.11,1:07:53.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,你說的對  對不起\N{\rENG}You were right. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.78,1:07:56.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,他不是我哥哥了\N{\rENG}He's not my brother anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.77,1:08:13.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,你有家人嗎?\N{\rENG}Do you have any family, Mr. Van Helsing?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.17,1:08:17.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,不曉得  我也想知道\N{\rENG}Not sure. I hope to find out someday.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.81,1:08:20.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,這就是我的動力\N{\rENG}That's what keeps me going.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.41,1:08:25.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 這才是你的動力 - 苦艾酒  很烈哦!\N{\rENG}- Here's to what keeps you going. - Absinthe. Strong stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.28,1:08:32.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,別碰到舌頭  否則的話…\N{\rENG}Don't let it touch your tongue. It'll knock you on your--
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.81,1:08:54.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,吸血鬼\N{\rENG}Vampire.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.38,1:08:58.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,吸血鬼!\N{\rENG}Vampires!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.69,1:09:07.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,我記起來了\N{\rENG}Now I remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.03,1:09:24.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,就算擁有一顆純潔虔誠的心\N{\rENG}"Even a man who is pure in heart And says his prayers by night
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.44,1:09:29.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,每逢月圓之夜\N{\rENG}"May become a wolf when the wolfbane blooms
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.54,1:09:32.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,也可能變成一個狼人\N{\rENG}"And the moon is shining bright
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.45,1:09:35.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,或是在日落後吸食人血\N{\rENG}"Or crave another's blood when the sun goes down
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.65,1:09:38.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,振翅而飛\N{\rENG}"And his body takes to flight"
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.86,1:10:20.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,下麵有怪物\N{\rENG}There's something down here.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.40,1:10:24.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,他會吃人\N{\rENG}And it's carnivorous.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.44,1:10:30.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,他看起來是人類\N{\rENG}Whatever it is, it appears to be human.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.84,1:10:39.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,他穿17號鞋 重164公斤\N{\rENG}I'd say he's a size 17. Around 360 pounds.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.38,1:10:42.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,高270公分\N{\rENG}8.5 to 9 feet tall.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.28,1:10:47.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,右腳有點跛 有三顆銅牙\N{\rENG}He has a bad gimp in his right leg and three copper teeth.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.29,1:10:49.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道?\N{\rENG}How do you know he has copper teeth?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.92,1:10:52.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,他就在你後面  快閃\N{\rENG}Because he's standing right behind you. Move!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.90,1:11:01.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,天啊!科學怪人\N{\rENG}Oh, my God! The Frankenstein monster!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.17,1:11:04.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,我才不是怪物\N{\rENG}Monster? Who's the monster here?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.37,1:11:08.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,我又沒做壞事\N{\rENG}I have done nothing wrong...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.41,1:11:11.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們卻想置我於死地\N{\rENG}and yet you and your kind all wish me dead!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.07,1:11:35.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,你想要什麼?\N{\rENG}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.60,1:11:38.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想活\N{\rENG}To exist.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.99,1:11:52.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,住手!\N{\rENG}Don't!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.39,1:11:53.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 一定要斃了他 - 等等\N{\rENG}- We must kill it. - Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.99,1:11:57.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,如果你們不想害死人類\N{\rENG}If you value your lives and the lives of your kind...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.83,1:12:00.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 最好把我給殺了 - 不\N{\rENG}- you will kill me. - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.23,1:12:03.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,德古拉一直想找我\N{\rENG}If Dracula finds me....
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.37,1:12:09.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,我是起死回生的關鍵\N{\rENG}I am the key to my father's machine.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.00,1:12:11.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,我是生命之鑰\N{\rENG}The key to life.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.47,1:12:15.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,我能讓吸血鬼後裔活過來\N{\rENG}Life for Dracula's children.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.41,1:12:17.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,他昨晚讓他們活過來\N{\rENG}He already awakened them last night.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.35,1:12:18.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,兩個\N{\rENG}Two.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.68,1:12:22.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,那只是一個吸血鬼新娘…\N{\rENG}And those were from only one bride.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.32,1:12:26.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,一胎生出來的孩子\N{\rENG}From one single birthing.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.45,1:12:29.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,上次他們也不能存活\N{\rENG}And they died as they did the last time he tried.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.89,1:12:37.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,只有我能讓他們獲得永生\N{\rENG}Only with me can he give them lasting life.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.93,1:12:40.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,還有更多嗎?\N{\rENG}There are more? More of those things?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.64,1:12:43.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,成千…\N{\rENG}Thousands.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.47,1:12:46.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,上萬\N{\rENG}Thousands more.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.69,1:13:01.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 不要 - 你也聽到他的話\N{\rENG}- No. - You heard what he said.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.72,1:13:04.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,消滅邪惡是我的使命和責任\N{\rENG}My life, my job is to vanquish evil.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.99,1:13:06.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的直覺很靈\N{\rENG}I can sense evil.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.66,1:13:09.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,邪惡力量造出…\N{\rENG}This thing, man, whatever it is...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.10,1:13:11.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,這個科學怪人\N{\rENG}evil may have created it, may have left its mark on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.67,1:13:15.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,他本身卻不邪惡  我不能殺他\N{\rENG}But evil does not rule it, so I cannot kill it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.14,1:13:17.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我可以 - 休想\N{\rENG}- I can. - Not while I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.04,1:13:25.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,你家人一直想消滅德古拉\N{\rENG}Your family has spent 400 years trying to kill Dracula.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.61,1:13:29.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,也許他能幫忙\N{\rENG}Maybe this poor creature can help us find a way.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.89,1:13:40.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,糟了  我們被發現了\N{\rENG}Oh, my God. He's seen us.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.26,1:13:42.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們一定會找到他\N{\rENG}Now they'll come for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.80,1:13:44.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,只憑我們兩個人阻止不了他們\N{\rENG}Neither you nor l will be able to stop them.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.80,1:13:48.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,我只要帶他到羅馬就安全\N{\rENG}If I can get him to Rome, we can protect him there.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.14,1:13:49.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,那幅畫活過來…\N{\rENG}And then the painting came alive...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.74,1:13:51.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,怪獸自相殘殺\N{\rENG}and the two creatures attacked each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.61,1:13:53.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 這代表什麼? - 不知道\N{\rENG}- What does it mean? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.57,1:13:56.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,卡爾  別盯著他看\N{\rENG}Listen, Carl, whatever you do, don't stare at him.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.18,1:14:00.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,我在盯著他看\N{\rENG}I'm staring at him.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.41,1:14:01.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,他是一個人嗎?\N{\rENG}Is that a man?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.85,1:14:04.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,他是七個人拼湊出來的\N{\rENG}Actually, seven men. Parts, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.09,1:14:06.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,我被他們抓到…\N{\rENG}By exposing me, you have condemned me!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.85,1:14:08.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,人類就會滅亡\N{\rENG}Me and all of humanity!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.72,1:14:11.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,德蘭斯斐尼亞駿馬…\N{\rENG}Nothing is faster than Transylvanian horses.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.33,1:14:13.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,比狼人更快\N{\rENG}Not even a werewolf.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.33,1:14:16.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,碰到別的怪物就沒轍\N{\rENG}Anything else, you're on your own.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.11,1:14:32.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 讓我走 - 你要走去哪兒?\N{\rENG}- Let me go. - Where are you going to go?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.91,1:14:34.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,照照鏡子吧!\N{\rENG}I don't know if you've seen a mirror lately...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.98,1:14:36.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,你很顯眼耶\N{\rENG}but you kind of stick out in a crowd.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.72,1:14:43.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,德蘭斯斐尼亞
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.39,1:14:48.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,喀爾巴阡山脈
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.71,1:14:59.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,布達佩斯
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.32,1:16:58.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,不能讓科學怪人喪命\N{\rENG}We must not let the creature be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.40,1:17:08.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,快去救科學怪人\N{\rENG}Save him! Save the monster!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.62,1:17:30.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,銀樁!\N{\rENG}Stakes!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.23,1:17:42.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,不!\N{\rENG}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.39,1:18:02.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,卡爾\N{\rENG}Carl
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.66,1:18:04.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的老天\N{\rENG}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.93,1:18:13.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,你在幹嘛?\N{\rENG}What are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.47,1:18:17.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,別放手!\N{\rENG}Don't let go!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.12,1:18:31.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,我能幫忙!\N{\rENG}I can help!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.62,1:18:33.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,你不會殺我?\N{\rENG}You won't kill me?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.09,1:18:35.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,你得趕快放開我\N{\rENG}Only if you don't hurry!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.37,1:19:20.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,快跳\N{\rENG}Jump!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.28,1:20:08.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,安娜\N{\rENG}Anna...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.96,1:20:17.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,原諒我\N{\rENG}forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.90,1:20:28.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們會再相見\N{\rENG}I will see you again.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.95,1:20:40.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,你殺了他\N{\rENG}You killed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.55,1:20:45.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,所以我才是殺人狂\N{\rENG}Now you know why they call me murderer.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.33,1:20:54.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,天啊!\N{\rENG}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.50,1:20:58.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,你被咬了\N{\rENG}You've been bitten.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.09,1:21:56.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,你害主人傷透腦筋\N{\rENG}So much trouble to my master. So much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.06,1:21:58.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,你要什麼?\N{\rENG}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.29,1:22:00.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,主人要跟你交換\N{\rENG}The master commands a trade.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.43,1:22:06.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,用安娜公主交換科學怪人\N{\rENG}The monster for the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.93,1:22:09.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,在大庭廣眾的地方\N{\rENG}Somewhere public. Lots of people.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.01,1:22:14.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,你主人不會…\N{\rENG}A place where your master will be less inclined...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.34,1:22:16.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,露出猙獰面目\N{\rENG}to expose his other side.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.88,1:22:21.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,明晚是萬聖夜\N{\rENG}Tomorrow night is All Hallows' Eve.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.32,1:22:27.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,布達佩斯有一場盛大化妝舞會\N{\rENG}Here in Budapest there is a wonderful masquerade ball.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.27,1:22:40.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你沒事吧? - 沒事\N{\rENG}- Are you all right? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.37,1:22:45.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,他被狼人…\N{\rENG}He has been bitten.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.11,1:22:47.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,咬了\N{\rENG}Bitten by a werewolf.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.08,1:22:52.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,你會變成你獵殺的怪物\N{\rENG}Now you will become that which you have hunted so passionately.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.72,1:23:01.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,很抱歉\N{\rENG}I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.96,1:23:05.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,希望別人也一樣會獵殺你\N{\rENG}May others be as passionate in their hunting of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.93,1:23:13.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,他在這兒很安全\N{\rENG}Well, they won't find him in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.47,1:23:15.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,這真是罪過\N{\rENG}I'm sure this is some sort of sin.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.27,1:23:17.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,別擔心  上帝會饒恕我們的 我們必須救出安娜\N{\rENG}God will forgive us. We need to save Anna.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.80,1:23:19.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,這頂帽子會不會太炫?\N{\rENG}You don't think the hat's a bit much?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.57,1:23:21.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 幫幫忙 - 好\N{\rENG}- Carl, help me! - Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.21,1:23:24.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,咱們破了幾誡呀?\N{\rENG}How many commandments can we break in one day?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.08,1:23:26.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,根據書上記載…\N{\rENG}Anyway, according to the book...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.11,1:23:29.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,你在第一個月圓才會變成狼人\N{\rENG}you won't turn into a werewolf until the rising of your first full moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.65,1:23:31.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,也就是兩天后\N{\rENG}That's two nights from now.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.05,1:23:34.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,這兩天你還有抵抗能力\N{\rENG}You'll still be able to fight Dracula's hold over you...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.22,1:23:35.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,直到兩天后的半夜\N{\rENG}until the final stroke of midnight.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.79,1:23:39.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我一點都不擔心 - 你應該害怕才對\N{\rENG}- So I have nothing to worry about. - My God, you should be terrified.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.13,1:23:40.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 多謝了 - 抱歉\N{\rENG}- Thanks. - Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.46,1:23:43.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,一定要在兩天內想出辦法\N{\rENG}We still have 48 hours to find a solution.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.70,1:23:45.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,你確定他出不去?\N{\rENG}You sure he can't get out of there?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.33,1:23:48.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,除非有死人頭幫忙\N{\rENG}Not without some help from the dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.22,1:25:16.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,當我的傀儡感覺如何?\N{\rENG}How does it feel to be a puppet on my string?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.46,1:25:19.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不會讓你交換我\N{\rENG}I won't let you trade me, Count.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.43,1:25:22.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不會交換你\N{\rENG}I have no intention of trading you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.03,1:25:25.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,我很瞭解范海辛\N{\rENG}And if I know Van Helsing, which I do...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.20,1:25:28.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,他也不會交換\N{\rENG}he is not planning on making a trade, either.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.37,1:25:32.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們都沒這麼容易打發\N{\rENG}Neither of us has ever settled for half.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.65,1:25:40.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們在那兒\N{\rENG}There they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.18,1:25:42.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,你讓我不寒而粟\N{\rENG}You make my skin crawl.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.22,1:25:48.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,我會讓你熱情如火\N{\rENG}This is not all I could do with your skin.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.93,1:26:00.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,幫我一個忙\N{\rENG}Carl, I need you to do something.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.37,1:26:02.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不會喜歡  對吧?\N{\rENG}I'm not gonna like this, am l?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.64,1:26:09.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,咱們真是速配\N{\rENG}Don't we make a lovely couple?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.31,1:26:10.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\rENG}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.88,1:26:13.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,我在找一個新娘\N{\rENG}I am looking for a new bride, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.98,1:26:17.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,美麗堅強\N{\rENG}Someone strong and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.06,1:26:31.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,你只要忍一忍痛\N{\rENG}One brief moment of pain...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.00,1:26:35.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們就能永遠在一起\N{\rENG}and we can be together forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.41,1:26:45.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,你沒有心跳\N{\rENG}You have no heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.41,1:26:50.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,也許你可以…\N{\rENG}Perhaps it just needs...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.05,1:26:53.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,讓我心動\N{\rENG}to be rekindled.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.28,1:27:21.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,安娜  醒醒\N{\rENG}Anna. Anna! Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.08,1:27:23.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,蓋布歐\N{\rENG}Gabriel.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.96,1:27:39.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,歡迎來到我的夏宮\N{\rENG}Welcome to my summer palace.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.87,1:27:44.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,主人  你看\N{\rENG}Master! Look, master!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.31,1:27:48.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們抓到他了\N{\rENG}We have him, master.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.95,1:27:54.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,怎樣會  活死人…\N{\rENG}You wretched undead...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.51,1:27:57.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,我會報仇的\N{\rENG}I shall have my revenge!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.35,1:28:00.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,我雖走過死亡蔭穀\N{\rENG}"Though I walk through the valley of the shadow of death...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.82,1:28:03.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,但是卻不怕邪惡\N{\rENG}"l shall fear no evil."
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.82,1:28:06.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們只是受詛咒的…\N{\rENG}You are nothing but damned bones...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.96,1:28:09.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,靈魂\N{\rENG}and damned souls...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.10,1:28:13.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,將受到地獄烈焰焚燒\N{\rENG}and will burn in the flames of Hell!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.97,1:28:22.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,事情終於搞定了\N{\rENG}Now that everything is as it should be...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.41,1:28:28.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,各位先生女士  容我介紹…\N{\rENG}Ladies and gentlemen, I give to you...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.75,1:28:32.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,范海辛\N{\rENG}Van Helsing!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.99,1:28:38.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,走吧!\N{\rENG}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.36,1:28:40.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,快呀!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.53,1:28:43.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rENG}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.24,1:28:52.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,我知道怎麼用這玩意了\N{\rENG}Now I know what it's for.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.67,1:28:55.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 怎麼走? - 那扇窗\N{\rENG}- Where are we going? - Through that window!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.29,1:29:15.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,你真是個天才\N{\rENG}Carl, you're a genius!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.86,1:29:18.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,我只是有一些勁爆道具\N{\rENG}A genius with access to unstable chemicals.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.14,1:29:32.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,跟他們說拜拜吧\N{\rENG}Say goodbye to your friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.50,1:29:55.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,我會找到你的 我對天發誓\N{\rENG}I'll find you! I'll get you back and set you free!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.64,1:29:57.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,我會去救你\N{\rENG}I swear to God!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.98,1:30:07.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我一定要救他 - 不行\N{\rENG}- I must save him. - No, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.21,1:30:08.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,為什麼?\N{\rENG}Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.38,1:30:11.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,我請示過羅馬教廷\N{\rENG}I cabled Rome earlier to apprise them of our situation.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.02,1:30:13.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 怎麼樣? - 就算你殺了吸血鬼\N{\rENG}- What did they say? - Even if you kill Dracula...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.62,1:30:16.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,一樣要毀了科學怪人\N{\rENG}Rome orders you to destroy Frankenstein as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.76,1:30:17.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,他並不邪惡\N{\rENG}He isn't evil.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.99,1:30:19.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們說他不是人\N{\rENG}But they say he isn't human, either.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.59,1:30:22.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們憑什麼這麼說?\N{\rENG}Do they know him? Have they spoken to him? Who are they to judge?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.63,1:30:25.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,他會被用來毀滅人類\N{\rENG}They want you to destroy him so he can never be used to harm humanity.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.93,1:30:28.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,那我呢?我也該死嗎?\N{\rENG}What of me? Did you tell them what I'm to become?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.30,1:30:30.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們有沒有教你怎麼殺我?\N{\rENG}Did they tell you how to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.14,1:30:32.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,如何正確的使用銀樁?\N{\rENG}The correct angle of the stake as it enters my heart?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.91,1:30:35.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,你該用多少銀彈?\N{\rENG}The exact measure of silver in each bullet?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.08,1:30:38.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 住手! - 我沒提起你\N{\rENG}- Stop! - No, I left you out!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.03,1:30:58.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,對不起\N{\rENG}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.34,1:31:05.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,我快變身了\N{\rENG}It's starting.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.49,1:31:23.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們把儀器帶到吸血鬼巢穴\N{\rENG}They must have taken all the equipment to Dracula's lair.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.39,1:31:25.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,不知道在哪兒\N{\rENG}Wherever that is.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.10,1:31:31.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,還有時間\N{\rENG}Look, there's still time.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.87,1:31:34.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,他要到晚上才能行動\N{\rENG}Dracula can't bring his children to life until the sun sets.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.70,1:31:35.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,只有兩小時\N{\rENG}The sun sets in two hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.97,1:31:38.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們花了四百年都找不到他\N{\rENG}We've been looking for him for more than 400 years!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.30,1:31:42.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,這次有我在  安啦!\N{\rENG}Yes, well, I wasn't around for those 400 years, now, was l?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.91,1:31:44.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,你發現什麼?\N{\rENG}Okay, Carl, what have you learned?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.84,1:31:48.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,德古拉是維拉瑞斯之子\N{\rENG}That Count Dracula was actually the son of Valerious the Elder.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.11,1:31:49.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,也就是你的祖先\N{\rENG}The son of your ancestor.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.72,1:31:51.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,大家都知道  還有呢?\N{\rENG}Everybody knows that. What else?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.75,1:31:55.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,根據文獻記載…\N{\rENG}All right. Well, according to this rubbing...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.29,1:31:57.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,他遭到謀殺\N{\rENG}it all started when Dracula was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.32,1:31:59.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 兇手是誰? - 不知道\N{\rENG}- Do you know who murdered him? - No,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.09,1:32:01.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,上面只提到上帝的左手\N{\rENG}there's just some vague reference to the Left Hand of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.79,1:32:05.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,1462年他死時…\N{\rENG}And in 1462, when Dracula died...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.63,1:32:08.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 和魔鬼交易 - 並被賜予新生\N{\rENG}- he made a covenant with the Devil. - And was given a new life.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.97,1:32:12.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,但是他必須吸食人血\N{\rENG}But the only way he could sustain that life was by drinking blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.07,1:32:14.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,讓我說完  好唄\N{\rENG}Excuse me. Are you going to let me tell the story?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.34,1:32:15.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\rENG}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.41,1:32:18.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,你的祖先因為這個不肖子…\N{\rENG}And your ancestor, having sired this evil creature...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.55,1:32:22.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,前往羅馬請求教廷寬恕\N{\rENG}went to Rome to seek forgiveness. That's when the bargain was made.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.92,1:32:24.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,他要殺死德古拉…\N{\rENG}He was to kill Dracula...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.28,1:32:27.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,才能延續家族香火\N{\rENG}in return for eternal salvation of his entire family...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.99,1:32:30.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,一直到你為止\N{\rENG}right down the line all the way to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.39,1:32:32.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,但是他無法對…\N{\rENG}But he couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.16,1:32:35.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,親生兒子下毒手\N{\rENG}As evil as Dracula was, my ancestor couldn't kill his own son.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.09,1:32:38.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,他把德古拉放逐到冰封城堡\N{\rENG}So he banished him to an icy fortress...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.50,1:32:41.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,送入一道一去不返的門\N{\rENG}sending him through a door from which there was no return.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.23,1:32:43.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 但是魔鬼給他翅膀 - 沒錯\N{\rENG}- And then the Devil gave him wings. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.20,1:32:46.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 這道門在哪裡? - 不知道\N{\rENG}- All right, so where is this door? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.57,1:32:51.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,你的祖先留下線索\N{\rENG}But when your ancestor couldn't kill his son, he left clues.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.58,1:32:55.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,好讓後代子孫完成任務\N{\rENG}So that future generations might do it for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.48,1:32:57.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,我父親就是在這裡…\N{\rENG}That must be what my father was looking for in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.85,1:32:59.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,尋找這道門的線索\N{\rENG}Clues to the door's location.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.95,1:33:01.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,門\N{\rENG}The door.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.92,1:33:05.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,我知道了\N{\rENG}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.13,1:33:07.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,你父親成天…\N{\rENG}You said your father spent hours...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.69,1:33:09.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,都盯著這幅畫\N{\rENG}staring at this painting, trying to find the lair.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.96,1:33:11.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想你是對的\N{\rENG}I think you were right. Quite literally.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.76,1:33:15.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,這就是那道門 只是他打不開\N{\rENG}I think this is the door. He just didn't know how to open it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.03,1:33:16.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,拉丁文\N{\rENG}Look. A Latin inscription.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.90,1:33:19.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,搞不好我會讀\N{\rENG}Maybe it works like the painting in the tower.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.07,1:33:23.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,是的話我父親早就打開了\N{\rENG}If this were a door, my father would have opened it long ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.34,1:33:27.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,少了一塊  讀不出來\N{\rENG}I can't finish the inscription. There's a piece missing.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.78,1:33:32.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,德蘭斯斐尼亞
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.85,1:33:35.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你父親沒有這個 - 你從哪兒來的?\N{\rENG}- Your father didn't have this. - Where did you get that?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.46,1:33:37.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,拼起來\N{\rENG}Carl, finish it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.50,1:33:47.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,以上帝之名打開此門\N{\rENG}In the name of God, open this door.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.51,1:34:01.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,一面鏡子\N{\rENG}A mirror.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.25,1:34:03.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,德古拉沒有倒影\N{\rENG}Dracula has no reflection in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.92,1:34:05.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,為什麼?\N{\rENG}But why?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.89,1:34:11.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,也許這對他來說並不是鏡子\N{\rENG}Maybe, to Dracula it's not a mirror at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.44,1:34:35.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,好冷  在下雪\N{\rENG}It's cold. And it's snowing.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.45,1:34:42.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,到另一邊見\N{\rENG}See you on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.66,1:34:47.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,小心點\N{\rENG}Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.00,1:35:30.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,德古拉堡\N{\rENG}Castle Dracula.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.62,1:36:23.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,最好想出一個計謀\N{\rENG}Do we have a plan?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.02,1:36:25.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,三個臭皮匠…\N{\rENG}Doesn't have to be Wellington's at Waterloo...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.29,1:36:26.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,勝過一個諸葛亮\N{\rENG}but some sort of plan would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.83,1:36:28.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們進去阻止德古拉\N{\rENG}We're going to stop Dracula.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.26,1:36:29.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,誰敢擋路就格殺勿論\N{\rENG}And kill anything in our way.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.00,1:36:32.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,祝你們好運喔!\N{\rENG}Well, you let me know how that goes.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.38,1:36:45.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,雖然這兒很暖和…\N{\rENG}Well, as grateful as I am to be out of the cold...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.68,1:36:48.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,不過這可不是好事\N{\rENG}that doesn't seem like a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.29,1:36:55.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,快走吧!\N{\rENG}We'd better get moving.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.70,1:37:09.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 這些全是… - 沒錯\N{\rENG}- So are all of those-- - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.74,1:37:11.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 裡面都是… - 對\N{\rENG}- And inside them are-- - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.87,1:37:15.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,從早到晚就知道使喚人\N{\rENG}Igor do this! Igor do that!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.14,1:37:20.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,怎麼會?不可能\N{\rENG}How did you find.... It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.82,1:37:27.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 求求你別殺我 - 為什麼?\N{\rENG}- Please don't kill me! - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.45,1:37:30.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,因為…\N{\rENG}Well, l....
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.70,1:37:43.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,主人醒來了\N{\rENG}My master has awakened.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.19,1:38:06.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 有解藥 - 什麼?\N{\rENG}- There is a cure. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.56,1:38:11.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,德古拉有狼人的解藥\N{\rENG}Dracula. He has a cure to remove the curse of the werewolf!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.96,1:38:16.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,快去找解藥救你自己\N{\rENG}Go, find the cure! Save yourself!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.68,1:38:29.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,快去找吧!\N{\rENG}Come on. You heard him. Let's find it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.65,1:38:31.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,他怎麼會有解藥?\N{\rENG}Wait. Why does Dracula have a cure?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.55,1:38:34.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我不在乎 - 我在乎\N{\rENG}- I don't care! - I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.42,1:38:37.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,他為什麼需要解藥?\N{\rENG}Why does he need one? Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.52,1:38:41.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,因為只有狼人能殺死他\N{\rENG}Because the only thing that can kill him is a werewolf.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.79,1:38:43.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,這就是那幅畫的意思\N{\rENG}The painting. That's what it meant.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.40,1:38:46.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,狼人一直都聽命于德古拉\N{\rENG}Dracula's been using werewolves to do his bidding for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.63,1:38:49.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,要是狼人對他反撲\N{\rENG}Yes, but if one ever had the will to turn on him, he'd need a cure...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.00,1:38:53.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,他就能把他變回普通人\N{\rENG}to remove the curse and make him human before it bit him.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.27,1:38:55.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,帶他們去…\N{\rENG}You're going to take these two...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.74,1:38:58.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 拿解藥 - 我才不去\N{\rENG}- and lead them to the antidote. - No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.48,1:39:01.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,我去  我去\N{\rENG}Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.51,1:39:04.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,午夜鐘聲一響…\N{\rENG}Here's the plan. When the bell begins to toll midnight...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.18,1:39:05.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,就殺死德古拉\N{\rENG}you'll be able to kill Dracula.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.55,1:39:06.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們會在同時…\N{\rENG}We just need to find the cure...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.95,1:39:08.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,把解藥給你\N{\rENG}and get it into you before the final stroke.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.96,1:39:10.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,你瘋啦? 這是什麼爛計畫?\N{\rENG}Are you insane? What kind of plan is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.82,1:39:13.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,要是你敢亂指路…\N{\rENG}If they even suspect you of misleading them...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.73,1:39:15.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,就斬斷他手指\N{\rENG}clip off one of his fingers.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.19,1:39:17.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我會斬斷他別的東西 - 解藥在…\N{\rENG}- I'll clip off something. - The tower over there...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.46,1:39:19.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 高塔上 - 另一個高塔有什麼?\N{\rENG}- that's where it is. - And what about the other tower?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.93,1:39:21.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 拿來 - 那裡是…\N{\rENG}- Give me that! - That is where...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.43,1:39:25.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,實驗室 我不敢騙你\N{\rENG}we reassembled the laboratory. Would I lie to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.94,1:39:27.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,你想活命就不敢\N{\rENG}Not if you wanted to live.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.61,1:39:32.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,如果在午夜鐘響前沒拿到解藥…\N{\rENG}Now, if I'm not cured by the twelfth stroke of midnight....
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.02,1:39:38.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我下不了手 - 你一定要殺我\N{\rENG}- I don't think I could. - You must.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.39,1:39:45.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,來吧!\N{\rENG}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.99,1:39:49.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,這計畫不好\N{\rENG}I don't like this plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.40,1:39:52.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒辦法  小心點\N{\rENG}We don't have a choice. Just don't get killed.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.10,1:39:53.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,你不懂\N{\rENG}You still don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.90,1:39:56.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不怕死\N{\rENG}It doesn't matter what happens to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.17,1:39:58.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,我只想救我全家\N{\rENG}We must save my family.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.54,1:40:01.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,如果你遲到… 拔腿就逃\N{\rENG}If you're late, run like hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.68,1:40:07.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,別遲到\N{\rENG}Don't be late.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.76,1:40:23.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,去吧!快去\N{\rENG}Now go. Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.99,1:40:52.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,走開  臭東西\N{\rENG}Get off me, you vermin from hell!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.43,1:40:59.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,閉嘴  這是你的使命\N{\rENG}What are you complaining about? This is why you were made!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.03,1:41:03.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,證明人類也能創造生命\N{\rENG}To prove that God is not the only one who can create life!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.84,1:41:08.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,你要讓我的孩子復活\N{\rENG}And now you must give that life to my children.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.57,1:41:10.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,抬起來!\N{\rENG}Up!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.02,1:42:25.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,在那裡\N{\rENG}There it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.89,1:42:32.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,我先去\N{\rENG}I'll go first.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.95,1:42:56.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,卡爾!\N{\rENG}Carl!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.75,1:43:01.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,去死吧!\N{\rENG}Stay as long as you like.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.05,1:43:04.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,你想整我  我先整死你\N{\rENG}You try to get lgor. Igor get you!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.90,1:43:51.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 快去拿呀! - 你去拿\N{\rENG}- Go ahead. Grab it. - You go ahead and grab it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.47,1:43:53.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,我才不要…\N{\rENG}If there's one thing I've learned...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.11,1:43:56.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,碰這種危險物質\N{\rENG}it's never to be the first to stick your hand in a viscous material.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.38,1:44:06.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 嚇到你們了? - 並沒有\N{\rENG}- Did I scare you? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.52,1:44:11.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,我猜我得用點狠招\N{\rENG}Then maybe I need to try a little harder.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.50,1:44:21.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,我就說很危險吧!\N{\rENG}Viscous material! What did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.23,1:44:23.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,快去拿\N{\rENG}Get it!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.74,1:44:33.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,好燙  好燙\N{\rENG}Hot.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.98,1:44:35.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 快一點! - 好\N{\rENG}- Come on! - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.25,1:44:38.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,快把解藥拿給范海辛 快去呀!\N{\rENG}We've got to get the antidote to Van Helsing! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.72,1:44:43.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,你想得美\N{\rENG}You can't go until I say you can go!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.62,1:44:45.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,快跑呀!\N{\rENG}Keep running, Carl!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.46,1:44:49.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,給我過來  領死吧!\N{\rENG}And I'll say you can go when you're dead!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.77,1:45:34.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,天啊!\N{\rENG}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.37,1:46:08.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,別過來  快去找解藥\N{\rENG}What are you doing? You must find the cure!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.07,1:46:10.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我的朋友正在找 - 朋友\N{\rENG}- My friends are doing it for me. - Friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.94,1:46:12.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,對  你需要朋友嗎?\N{\rENG}Yes. You want one?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.71,1:46:15.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,我打不開 這會有點痛\N{\rENG}I can't unscrew the bolts. This is gonna hurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.41,1:46:17.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,我習慣了\N{\rENG}I am accustomed to pain.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.38,1:46:19.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,這代表你活著\N{\rENG}It lets you know you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.17,1:46:39.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,賜給我生命\N{\rENG}Give me life!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.65,1:46:58.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,再來一次我的孩子就會復活\N{\rENG}One more bolt and my young will live.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.94,1:47:14.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,就快好了\N{\rENG}You're almost out, my friend!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.88,1:49:33.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,救救我\N{\rENG}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.95,1:49:36.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,你應該死的\N{\rENG}But you're supposed to die.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.72,1:49:39.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想活\N{\rENG}I want to live.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.92,1:49:43.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,好吧!\N{\rENG}All right!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.63,1:49:50.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,你死了…\N{\rENG}Be happy in the knowledge...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.90,1:49:55.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,我會替你收屍\N{\rENG}that I shall weep over your dead body.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.04,1:50:01.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,撐著點\N{\rENG}Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.11,1:50:04.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,我來救你\N{\rENG}I'll swing you loose!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.51,1:50:41.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,你來晚了\N{\rENG}You are too late, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:41.88,1:50:44.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的孩子復活了\N{\rENG}My children live.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.48,1:50:47.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,那麼我只好殺了你\N{\rENG}Then the only way to kill them is to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.15,1:50:49.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒錯\N{\rENG}Correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.12,1:50:53.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,好吧!\N{\rENG}So be it.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:57.53,1:50:58.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,一\N{\rENG}One.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.57,1:51:07.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,不  不可能\N{\rENG}No, this cannot be.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:21.49,1:51:25.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們本來是同一國的\N{\rENG}We are both part of the same grand game, Gabriel.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.49,1:51:29.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,不必變成死對頭\N{\rENG}But we need not find ourselves on opposite sides of the board.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.14,1:52:20.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,快去救范海辛\N{\rENG}Go! Go and help Van Helsing!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.62,1:52:26.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,快點!\N{\rENG}Now!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.25,1:52:28.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,謝謝你\N{\rENG}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.61,1:53:00.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的天呀! 我需要幫忙\N{\rENG}Oh, my God! Anna, I need a little help!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.79,1:53:05.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,快點!\N{\rENG}Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.97,1:53:18.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,丟過來\N{\rENG}Throw it to me, Carl!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.00,1:53:50.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,你跟我一樣被人利用\N{\rENG}You are being used, Gabriel, as was l.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:50.97,1:53:53.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,你也可以逃走\N{\rENG}But I escaped. So can you.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.48,1:54:38.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,安娜  親愛的\N{\rENG}Anna, my love...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:38.28,1:54:42.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,你的鮮血讓我青春永駐\N{\rENG}it is your blood that shall keep me beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.55,1:54:44.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,去死吧!\N{\rENG}What do you think of that?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:48.96,1:54:51.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,你要殺人就快下手\N{\rENG}I think if you're going to kill someone, kill them.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:51.60,1:54:54.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,廢話少說\N{\rENG}Don't stand there talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:18.06,1:55:19.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,你不懂嗎?\N{\rENG}Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.76,1:55:24.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們可以成為好友 好搭檔\N{\rENG}We could be friends. Partners!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.26,1:55:27.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,最佳戰友\N{\rENG}Brothers-in-arms!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:57.63,1:56:02.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,我當年就是被你殺死的\N{\rENG}Did I mention that it was you who murdered me?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.73,1:56:06.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,身為上帝的左手\N{\rENG}It must be such a burden. Such a curse...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.34,1:56:10.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,是多麼沉重的負擔和詛咒\N{\rENG}to be the Left Hand of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:12.61,1:56:15.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,我只想獲得永生\N{\rENG}All I want is life, Gabriel.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.01,1:56:18.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,延續我的香火\N{\rENG}The continuation of my kind.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:18.55,1:56:22.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,拿回我的戒指\N{\rENG}And perhaps the return of my ring.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:26.69,1:56:29.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,別害怕\N{\rENG}Don't be afraid, Gabriel. Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:31.03,1:56:36.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,我會把你的命和記憶還給你\N{\rENG}I shall give you back your life, your memory.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:37.14,1:56:39.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,有些事忘了最好\N{\rENG}Some things are better left forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:13.04,1:57:14.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,上帝保佑\N{\rENG}For God!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.38,1:57:25.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,上帝原諒我\N{\rENG}God forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:59.72,1:58:01.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,她死了\N{\rENG}She's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:57.91,1:59:01.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,讓她安息吧! 主啊! 願你的榮光…\N{\rENG}"Eternal rest grant unto her, Oh, Lord, and let perpetual light...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:01.25,1:59:03.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,照亮她的靈魂…\N{\rENG}"shine upon her. On her soul and the souls of all...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:11.59,1:59:13.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,照亮她的靈魂…\N{\rENG}"On her soul and the souls of all...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:13.46,1:59:17.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,忠實信徒得到寬恕…\N{\rENG}"the dead faithful have mercy.... "

